news.title: West Bengal government to soon auction several land parcels in Alipore
news.para: The Housing Infrastructure Development Corporation (Hidco) has fixed a starting bid price of Rs 236.7 crore for a 5.6 acre plot at the rate of Rs 42.3 crore per acre.

news.title: Maharashtra government approves ULPIN for land parcels, rollout next month
news.para: Confirming the development, state settlement commissioner N K Sudhanshu told TOI that a GR (government resolution) had been issued on the Unique Land Parcel Identification Number (ULPIN).

news.title: Land sold after undertaking development activities should attract 18% GST: Madhya Pradesh AAAR
news.para: Any land sold after undertaking development activities such as providing water line, electricity or sanitation facility should attract 18% GST, Madhya Pradesh AAAR ruled.
